name: Weddingdates
tag_list: weddings, wedding-planning, hotels, hospitality, wedding-venues, wedding-reception
overview:
WeddingDates.ie is a unique website that allows engaged couples to select their chosen wedding date and the county in Ireland where they want to get married, and get back an interactive listing of hotels with reception availability on that date.

With detailed hotel descriptions, large format photos, and downloadable brochures and menus, there’s no better way to find the perfect setting for a perfect day.

WeddingDates.ie connects hotel and wedding venues to engaged couples and provides them with qualified leads to view the property before deciding on their wedding venue. With couples spending upwards of â‚¬10,000 on their wedding venue alone, weddings are a major revenue source for hotels and venues.
